    "solution": "<p>In aqueous medium the reaction follows $$\\mathrm{S_N 1}$$ mechanism majorly</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1lwbjw73x/393c202f-082e-4e53-b9d8-9eb03712d9be/f6107ad0-14c6-11ef-a0f4-45babcaa12d2/file-1lwbjw73y.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1lwbjw73x/393c202f-082e-4e53-b9d8-9eb03712d9be/f6107ad0-14c6-11ef-a0f4-45babcaa12d2/file-1lwbjw73y.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"JEE Main 2024 (Online) 6th April Evening Shift Chemistry - Hydrocarbons Question 41 English Explanation\"></p>",
